{"tid":303773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【七一大遊行當日維園地圖】","createTime":"2017-06-30T12:07:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T08:49:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a0ab2480de7514c1de2c0db24be75f043950570b","tid":303773,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T12:07:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/?ref=br_rs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCivilHumanRightsFront%2F%3Fref%3Dbr_rs&d=Kfcaz5XCad%2BQwKRNpnvvq7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=06339658\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/?ref=br_rs</a><br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線 Civil Human Rights Front<br />\nJune 28 at 6:45pm &middot; <br />\n<br />\n【七一大遊行當日維園地圖】<br />\n大家請留意七一大遊行，救護站、輪椅人士等候處、主台、回收桶等地點的位置，以及銅鑼灣和天后進入維園的人流走向。<br />\n<br />\n記得帶備充足的水份及適量輕便糧食參與七一遊行，預防酷暑和補充能量。<br />\n<br />\n48 shares"},{"pid":"6df67adcb0c18d7edd0155d1d44dafbf0806fb4f","tid":303773,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T12:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-0/p526x395/19452824_1406243786089675_1117013394190430894_o.jpg?oh=88c538cb1f68dad18acabd90d91693f0&amp;oe=59C4019C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-0%2Fp526x395%2F19452824_1406243786089675_1117013394190430894_o.jpg%3Foh%3D88c538cb1f68dad18acabd90d91693f0%26oe%3D59C4019C&h=7e5ac17a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e66971d78967ea16b154b2ac3828c6d8d4b6d1d","tid":303773,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T12:08:51.000Z","msg":"黑衫"},{"pid":"77eb33d4b948f5d3ff7f76ee322a62f18ce3f9ae","tid":303773,"uid":49197,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T12:09:43.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"483b1f205f0d9165611992158668bf29313a0c15","tid":303773,"uid":4942,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20